{"id":568357,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Little_(footballer)","text":"e=\"preserve\">Robert John \"Johnny\" Little (7 July 1930 \u2013 18 January 2017) was a Scottish footballer. He played as a defender. He played for Queen's Park, Rangers, Morton and the Scotland national team.\nLittle was born in Calgary, Alberta, Canada. He moved to Scotland at a young age and grew up in Millport of Great Cumbrae.\nLittle died on 18 January 2017 at the age of 86.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Scottish_people","surface_form":"Scottish","offset":79},{"uri":"Association_football","surface_form":"footballer","offset":88},{"uri":"Defender_(association_football)","surface_form":"defender","offset":115},{"uri":"Queen%27s_Park_F.C.","surface_form":"Queen's Park","offset":139},{"uri":"Rangers_F.C.","surface_form":"Rangers","offset":153},{"uri":"Greenock_Morton_F.C.","surface_form":"Morton","offset":162},{"uri":"Scotland_national_football_team","surface_form":"Scotland national team","offset":177},{"uri":"Calgary","surface_form":"Calgary","offset":220},{"uri":"Alberta","surface_form":"Alberta","offset":229},{"uri":"Canada","surface_form":"Canada","offset":238},{"uri":"Millport%2C_Cumbrae","surface_form":"Millport","offset":297},{"uri":"Great_Cumbrae","surface_form":"Great Cumbrae","offset":309}]}